Package: cfcdae
Title: Companion to a First Course in Design and Analysis of
        Experiments
Version: 1.4-11
Authors@R: person("Gary W.","Oehlert",email="gary@umn.edu", role=c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A collection of functions and data to accompany the book
	_A First Course in Design and Analysis of Experiments_, second edition,
	by Gary W. Oehlert. Some functions have analogs in other packages
	(e.g., interaction plots, pairwise comparisons, AICc) and
	some appear to be unique (e.g., side by side plots, plot for pairwise
	comparisons).
Imports: mvtnorm, pbkrtest, nlme, lme4, stats, DoE.base
